# SilverStripe Requirements Checker

This script will check your server environment to make sure it is configured correctly
for SilverStripe (http://silverstripe.org).

## Using

 1. Unpack the source files to somewhere in your webroot, e.g. /var/www/ssreqcheck
 2. Fire up a browser and point to that file, e.g. http://localhost/ssreqcheck/index.php

